36
00:02:09,538 --> 00:02:11,798
than at this ear, which is another cue that the brain uses

37
00:02:11,838 --> 00:02:14,699
to tell you where that is in the room. Really great spatialized

38
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,900
