00:05:00,976 --> 00:05:03,678
going to talk a little bit about this at the very end as well.

92
00:05:04,058 --> 00:05:06,840
The best VR experiences that we're going to see aren't going

93
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,943
to be adaptations of existing media forms. They're going to be

