00:07:56,151 --> 00:07:58,954
motion sickness is narrowing the FOV while you're moving.

145
00:07:59,735 --> 00:08:03,358
generally speaking we're not likely to get motion sick when we're watching a television

146
00:08:03,398 --> 00:08:07,681
because there's a small region of motion but we have the room around us to anchor us in space.

147
00:08:08,241 --> 00:08:13,445
So some of the experiences you might have seen narrow the field of view and bring in this ring

148
00:08:13,485 --> 00:08:17,708
of black around you while you're moving forward and then slowly move that out again when you

149
00:08:17,748 --> 00:08:22,212
stop. And the reality is most people don't even notice this or maybe they notice it at first but

150
00:08:22,232 --> 00:08:25,755
then they just get used to it and it really doesn't bother them but it allows them to anchor

151
00:08:25,795 --> 00:08:26,635
themselves in space.

