00:08:27,356 --> 00:08:29,517
In Google we're using some applications where rather than

153
00:08:29,557 --> 00:08:32,960
bringing in black, we actually bring in a gray grid that's

154
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:37,383
locked to the frame of the room to give you that sense of

155
00:08:37,443 --> 00:08:41,285
spatial coherence. Next, when you're teleporting, make sure

156
00:08:41,325 --> 00:08:43,567
you're teleporting to a psychologically safe location.

157
00:08:44,067 --> 00:08:46,349
It really sucks when you teleport and you have like a

