00:08:46,509 --> 00:08:48,711
wall right in front of you. Especially in a lot of our

159
00:08:48,731 --> 00:08:50,752
experiences where we don't even have textures on these walls,

160
00:08:51,152 --> 00:08:51,693
it's just like...

161
00:08:52,538 --> 00:08:57,580
